==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Insinuating
<hw>In*sin"u*a`ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Winding,
creeping, or flowing in, quietly or stealthily; suggesting; winning
favor and confidence insensibly.</def> <rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His address was courteous, and even <qex>insinuating</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Prescott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insinuatingly</ent>⟦br⟧
